---
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
layout: posts-index
---
<div class="main grid">	
    <div class="intro">
      <p>Somewhere between a blog and a journal, this digital garden is a place to think and learn through writing and share early ideas.</p>
      
      <h2 class="small-text section-heading">elsewhere</h2>    
      <ol> 
        <li>
          <a href="/">are.na</a><br> <span class="grey">collecting and connecting ideas (my external brain)</span>
        <li>
          <a href="#">montaigne</a><br> 
          <span class="grey">a microwebsite of good sentences and paragraphs</span>
        </li>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

<div class="wide">
  <h2 class="small-text section-heading">all posts</h2>    
  <ol reversed class="postlist" style="counter-reset: start-from {{ (postslistCounter or collections.posts.length) + 1 }}">
  {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    <li class="postlist-item{% if post.url == url %} postlist-item-active{% endif %}">
      <p>
        <time class="postlist-date" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}"><span>
        {{ post.date | readableDate("dd LLL yyyy") }}</span>
        </time>
      </p> 
      <p> 
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="postlist-link">
        {% if post.data.title %}
          {{ post.data.title }}
        {% else %}
          <code>{{ post.url }}</code>
        {% endif %}
        </a>
      </p> 
      {# <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p> #}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</div>
